      <title>意大利计划对最赚钱的公司征收更多税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/italy-aims-to-get-more-tax-out-of-its-most-profitable-companies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利财政部长吉安卡洛·乔尔盖蒂表示，意大利计划对那些在近年来的经济动荡中获益最多的公司提高税收，以帮助降低该国的预算赤字。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/italy-aims-to-get-more-tax-out-of-its-most-profitable-companies</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 12:15:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利比亚恢复石油生产，结束严重危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/libya-to-restart-oil-production-ending-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[利比亚于周四恢复石油生产，在该国政治僵局缓解后，每天向全球市场输送数十万桶石油。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/libya-to-restart-oil-production-ending-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 11:34:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
